text: Jana Hlaváčová (26 March 1938 – 13 January 2024) was a Czech actress. She was born in Prague. Her best known role was in the 2007 movie Operace Silver A. Hlaváčová died on 13 January 2024, at the age of 85. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Czech movie actors Category:Czech television actors Category:Czech stage actors Category:Actors from Prague
